According to Trac N4, the road has been closed between the Machado Plaza and weighbridge after a truck carrying explosives was involved in an accident. The accident was reported by Trac at 04:50 this morning, however their most recent update just after 06:00 advised that the N4 remains closed. Motorists are asked to travel via Lydenburg or Barberton instead. Traffic delays of 3 hours have been estimated.